sentence.text: Furthermore, we identified some potential lung cancer driver genes, such as negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II, G1/S transition of mitotic cell cycle, SLC2A1, protein phosphorylation, and CDC20, whose expression is significantly upregulated in lung cancer, and the copy number of these genes is amplified in the genome of patients with lung cancer.
